# Seller Dashboard Rules

Seller dashboard is an operational/business interface.

Seller experience should feel:
- productive
- operational
- easy to manage inventory
- analytics-oriented
- scalable

Seller modules include:
- Dashboard Overview
- Networks
- Inventory
- Cards Upload
- Orders
- Wallet
- Withdrawals
- Analytics
- Settings

Seller workflows should prioritize:
- inventory visibility
- upload simplicity
- sales tracking
- financial clarity
- operational efficiency

Always support:
- filtering
- search
- pagination
- bulk actions where useful
- status management
- upload workflows

Use reusable:
- dashboard tables
- stats cards
- forms
- upload components
- analytics widgets

Avoid:
- admin-level complexity
- cluttered navigation
- duplicated layouts

Seller dashboard should be responsive and mobile-usable.
